query: SELECT COUNT(*) as total_duplicates FROM (SELECT county, parcelId, COUNT(*) as dup_count FROM properties WHERE parcelId IS NOT NULL AND parcelId != '' GROUP BY county, parcelId HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) as duplicates
